title: Amazing Reincarnation
description: A shitty previous life with shitty looks meant he died a virgin. Because he lived his life as a goody two shoes, he was able to be reincarnated thanks to afterlife policy and the help of a Grim Reaper named Ahn Soojung. This is the story of how he finally gets to do everything he couldn't in his previous life, all in this amazing reincarnation.
author: Shicamuns
